data.description: If you love and appreciate historical homes?, then why not own one of your own!? Look no further. This home has a majestic feel as you enter the house. It was built in 1905 and offers 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and a finished attic that could be used for a 4th bedroom or a game room, workout, hobby or Movie room. The kitchen boasts upper end stainless steel appliances and granite countertops.   The Sunroom can be used as an office, a reading or hobby room or even a workout room...  ...Who doesn't love an in-ground pool? and an outdoor gathering place for entertaining and BBQ's - this home has it.!!!....  And.....the home comes complete with a 1 bedroom, 1 bath Casita or Guest quarters. The workshop has power, and the storage shed is a plus. All this nestled in a lovely private backyard.  Hurry! make an appointment to see this historical beauty...and bring your earnest money check....just incase you love it...IT WON'T LAST LONG!!
